<i> You must be mad, girlie.</i>

00:23:05.449 --> 00:23:07.552
<i> You know it's about
 2,000 miles,</i>

00:23:07.552 --> 00:23:10.455
six months of hard walkin'.

00:23:10.455 --> 00:23:12.690
You want to die out there
or something?

00:23:12.690 --> 00:23:14.926
